'''Ableɣ''' d amsektay [[tasengama|asangam]] i [[akat|wakat]] n taɣult i d-ttaṭṭaf kra n tfekka deg kra n wadeg, Ableɣ yemgarad ɣef [[tajumma|wenrar]], acku anrar iga d asmektay n tɣult tasenseggawt (2D), ma d ableɣ iga d asmektay n tɣult [[Akerseggaw|takerseggawt]]. Amedya, I wsiden n ubleɣ n [[Agasas|ugasas]] ad [[akfud|nekfed]] anrar n yiwen seg wudmawen-is ɣef tiddi. Ableɣ ur yeqqin ara ɣer [[Takura|tkura]] neɣ ɣer [[azuk|wazuk]] maca iga d taskant seg teskanin n [[tanga|tenga]] tisimanin acku iga d tajumma kan ɣef wacu i d-teẓẓun tfekka, dɣa ma tella [[tineẓẓi|tneẓẓi-ines]] teflal ad yili tkura-ines meqqer ɣas ma yella ubleɣ-is meẓẓiy. s wanecta tineẓẓi d ubleɣ zemren ad gucclen takuramaca ur ila ara (ur yesɛi ara) atig iman-is deg usiden n tkura,ma d azuk iga kan d tadusi n welday (ajbad) i ṭṭafarent tfekkiwin anda ig mgarad seg wadeg ɣer wayeṭ, amedya: tifekkiwin deg [[Yebter]] ẓẓay-it ɣef tfekkiwin deg [[Tagnit|tegnit]] acku dinna yulek i tdusi n welday meqqren.<br/>
Azamul n ubleɣ d V, yettwakat s [[Tigget n usekti|tiggtin]] tusligin, amedya: m³ neɣ cm³ neɣ mm³.

Ableɣ n ugasas yettwakat s 3 n iseggiwen idiganen: [[teɣzi (tusnakt)|Teɣzi]], [[Tehri]] d [[Tiddi]]. Ableɣ yettusemres deg tenfalit n tɣawsiwin timdettiyin am [[asfer|wesfer]] d tmuskiwin ... Atg, acku tiɣawsiwin-a yakk lant teɣzi d tehri d tiddi.
* Ableɣ n ugasas = teɣzi × tehri × tiddi^3
* Ableɣ n umsadaɣ n iserman = teɣzi × tehri × tiddi
* Ableɣ n uzamug = (tajumma n uzadur × 3) × tiddi

